//import './My-Style.css'

import React from 'react'
import { IonPage, IonCard, IonHeader, IonToolbar, IonBackButton, IonContent, IonTitle, IonButtons, IonTextarea,
    IonCardContent, IonLabel, IonItem, IonInput} from '@ionic/react'

import { addItems } from '../components/frontend/add-items'
import { beansDefault } from '../components/objects/default-values'


const array =  [
    ['Bohne', true],
    ['Röster', true],
    ['Kommentar', true]]

export const AddBeans = () => {
    return (
        <IonPage>
            <IonHeader>
                <IonToolbar>
                        <IonButtons slot='start'>
                           <IonBackButton defaultHref='home'/>
                        </IonButtons>
                <IonTitle>Bohne erfassen</IonTitle>
                </IonToolbar>
                </IonHeader>
            <IonContent>
                <IonCard>
                    <IonCardContent>
                        {addItems(array)}

                    </IonCardContent>
                </IonCard>
            </IonContent>
        </IonPage>
    )
}
